    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const successfulReminders = $input.all();\nconst failedReminders = $node[\"Log Missing Phone\"].all() || [];\n\nconst summary = {\n  executionTime: new Date().toISOString(),\n  totalProcessed: successfulReminders.length + failedReminders.length,\n  successfulSMS: successfulReminders.length,\n  failedSMS: failedReminders.length,\n  successfulEmployees: successfulReminders.map(item => ({\n    name: item.json['Employee'],\n    id: item.json['Employee Id'],\n    shiftTime: `${item.json['Date']} ${item.json['In']}-${item.json['Out']}`,\n    client: item.json['Client']\n  })),\n  failedEmployees: failedReminders.map(item => ({\n    name: item.json.employeeName,\n    id: item.json.employeeId,\n    reason: item.json.status,\n    shiftInfo: item.json.shiftInfo\n  }))\n};\n\nreturn [{ json: summary }];"
      },
      "id": "dab639f9-7229-454b-9428-5624a30480fa",
      "name": "Create Summary Report",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        1968,
        1584
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# 📱 SMS Shift Reminder System Setup\n\n## Required Configuration:\n\n### 1. Google Sheets\n- Replace `YOUR_SHIFT_SCHEDULE_SHEET_ID` in \"Get Shift Schedule\" node\n- Replace `YOUR_EMPLOYEE_CONTACTS_SHEET_ID` in \"Get Employee Contacts\" node\n- Sheet IDs are found in the Google Sheets URL after `/d/`\n\n### 2. Twilio\n- Update `twilioPhoneNumber` in \"Configuration\" node\n- Format: +1234567890 (with country code)\n\n### 3. Credentials\n- Add Google Sheets OAuth2 credentials\n- Add Twilio API credentials (Account SID & Auth Token)\n\n### 4. Timezone & Timing\n- Adjust `timezone` in Configuration node (default: America/Chicago)\n- Modify `hoursBeforeShift` to change reminder timing (default: 24 hours)\n- Change schedule in \"Daily Schedule Trigger\" (default: 9 AM daily)",
        "height": 640,
        "width": 564,
        "color": 7
      },
      "id": "511b70ce-071e-4330-9d3e-c1cd7effc599",
      "name": "Setup Instructions",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -576,
        976
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## ✨ Key Features\n\n- **Smart Date Parsing**: Handles multiple date/time formats\n- **Error Handling**: Continues on failures, logs issues\n- **Phone Validation**: Formats US numbers automatically\n- **Duplicate Prevention**: Ensures one SMS per shift\n- **Debug Mode**: Enable in Configuration for detailed logs\n- **Comprehensive Reporting**: Summary of all sent/failed reminders\n- **Timezone Support**: Handles CST and other timezones\n- **Status Filtering**: Only sends for \"Scheduled\" shifts",
        "height": 346,
        "width": 400,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "58838b37-b9b8-46fc-96e6-4293c0ef85e2",
      "name": "Key Features",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -288,
        1680
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🔄 Data Flow\n\n1. **Daily Trigger** runs at scheduled time\n2. **Fetch Data** from both Google Sheets\n3. **Merge** employee contacts with shift data\n4. **Filter** shifts ~24 hours away\n5. **Validate** phone numbers exist\n6. **Format** phone numbers for SMS\n7. **Send SMS** via Twilio\n8. **Remove Duplicates** to prevent double-sends\n9. **Generate Summary** report of results",
        "height": 282,
        "width": 350,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "3611f792-2fce-4b99-be5b-5e1128c842ed",
      "name": "Workflow Overview",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
