    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## SMS Shift Reminder Workflow\n\n### Configuration Required:\n1. **Google Sheets IDs**: Replace `YOUR_SHIFT_SCHEDULE_SHEET_ID` and `YOUR_EMPLOYEE_CONTACTS_SHEET_ID` with your actual Google Sheet IDs\n2. **Twilio Phone Number**: Update in Configuration node\n3. **Reminder Timing**: Adjust `hoursBeforeShift` in Configuration node (default: 24 hours)\n4. **Timezone**: Set your local timezone in Configuration node (default: America/Chicago for CST)\n\n### How it works:\n- Runs daily at 9 AM (adjustable in Schedule Trigger)\n- Fetches all shifts and employee contacts\n- Filters shifts occurring 24 hours from now\n- Sends personalized SMS reminders via Twilio\n- Logs any missing phone numbers for review",
        "height": 250,
        "width": 600
      },
      "id": "40e61224-1703-42aa-ba02-fe58f50284ea",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -1824,
        2288
      ],
      "disabled": true
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Date Filtering Logic\n\nThe Code node checks if shifts are within a 1-hour window of the configured reminder time.\n\nFor example, if `hoursBeforeShift` = 24:\n- Shifts 23.5 to 24.5 hours away will be matched\n- This accounts for the workflow running once daily\n\nAdjust the window in the Filter node if needed.",
        "height": 150,
        "width": 350
      },
      "id": "dc1af069-eab8-4f70-a2ec-5117d161d15b",
      "name": "Sticky Note 2",
